  "texts": [
    "We used Cytoscape [61], an open-source software platform, to visualize the network (Fig 13).",
    "With the confidence factor of each relation used as its corresponding weight, an arc appears thicker for higher CF e a e t.",
    "The node size corresponds directly to the in-degree of the node.",
    "The GRN can help understand the complex regulatory mechanisms governing gene expression in E. coli.",
    "These networks can also serve as prior knowledge for reconstructing GRNs using more advanced computational methodologies and address the excessive computational overhead."
  ]
